94
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:35,379
Just Big Bro Lei?

95
00:06:35,379 --> 00:06:37,359
And...

96
00:06:37,359 --> 00:06:39,949
Wan Wan!

97
00:06:39,949 --> 00:06:42,679
