100
00:06:47,169 --> 00:06:48,819
Great!

101
00:06:48,819 --> 00:06:52,849
- Little Qi has grown up.
- But he's not as great as Big Bro Gang.

102
00:06:52,849 --> 00:06:56,400
You took Si Qi in without hesitation.

103
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:02,599
You both joined the same club

104
00:07:02,599 --> 00:07:06,670
- but have completely different personalities.
- What do you mean by "club"?

105
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:12,220
Jin Yu Zhen was Big Bro Gang's junior at the university.

106
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:16,529
You're shocked, right? They went to the same university.

107
00:07:16,529 --> 00:07:19,440
Big Bro Gang is very easy-going.

108
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:22,850
But look at Jin Yu Zhen.

109
00:07:47,850 --> 00:07:49,869
No.

110
00:07:49,869 --> 00:07:54,419
- Wh-Wh-What?
- I won't buy ingredients for now.

111
00:07:54,419 --> 00:07:58,099
I will buy some if I need to cook at home.

112
00:07:58,099 --> 00:07:59,809
Why?

113
00:07:59,809 --> 00:08:03,099
Your goal isn't to become a chef.

114
00:08:03,099 --> 00:08:05,609
I just want to help out.

115
00:08:05,609 --> 00:08:09,349
You can help them out at the craft workshop.

116
00:08:09,349 --> 00:08:11,679
I can't help Big Bro Lei.

117
00:08:11,679 --> 00:08:15,089
Big Sis Qian... also doesn't need me.

118
00:08:15,089 --> 00:08:18,130
Here. Let me see your hand.

119
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,699
