139
00:09:28,869 --> 00:09:32,140
I would like to introduce Chairman Mai to...

140
00:09:32,870 --> 00:09:34,549
You did pretty well.

141
00:09:34,549 --> 00:09:37,069
We are about to begin the production stage now.

142
00:09:37,069 --> 00:09:39,959
Of course. I have my feet on the ground.

143
00:09:39,959 --> 00:09:43,359
I'm nowhere near as sly as you.

144
00:09:43,359 --> 00:09:45,589
- Me?
- Are you confused?

145
00:09:45,589 --> 00:09:47,129
I was just thinking, how come you were so capable?

146
00:09:47,129 --> 00:09:49,449
How were you able to connect with such a large company?

147
00:09:49,449 --> 00:09:52,309
Turns out, you know Mai Zheng Xiong.

148
00:09:52,309 --> 00:09:56,109
