149
00:09:56,109 --> 00:09:59,609
Just like a father would toward a son.

150
00:09:59,609 --> 00:10:01,409
Networking is essential.

151
00:10:01,409 --> 00:10:05,870
Also, weren't you guys trying to win the bet this way before?

152
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:12,080
Hey, sorry.

153
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:19,079
The Kryptonian thing that I mentioned

154
00:10:19,079 --> 00:10:21,180
