157
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:36,180
That's fine.

158
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:39,320
I mean it.

159
00:10:52,940 --> 00:10:55,249
I don't think it will work.

160
00:10:55,249 --> 00:10:56,890
Why not?

161
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:01,109
Do you live-streamers

162
00:11:01,109 --> 00:11:05,329
- have standards this high?
- Show him how to do it.

163
00:11:05,329 --> 00:11:07,080
