164
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,620
Your turn.

165
00:11:12,810 --> 00:11:15,190
I'm quitting.

166
00:11:16,419 --> 00:11:18,909
Why do you sound so girly?

167
00:11:18,909 --> 00:11:21,539
