168
00:11:21,539 --> 00:11:25,429
You have no idea how strong of an aura our boss has.

169
00:11:25,429 --> 00:11:27,869
- Do you want to get married?
- Yes.

170
00:11:27,869 --> 00:11:30,219
Then you have to have a stronger aura than your boss's.

171
00:11:30,219 --> 00:11:32,949
If you can't beat your boss, you'll never be able to get married.

172
00:11:32,949 --> 00:11:36,069
I'll tell you what, tell your boss that nobody can change my drafts.

173
00:11:36,069 --> 00:11:38,960
Find someone else if you want to change them. I'm not doing it!

174
00:11:42,030 --> 00:11:46,310
I believe Big Sis Qian has the most powerful aura.

175
00:11:58,580 --> 00:12:00,889
These are the ores the design studio currently has.

176
00:12:00,889 --> 00:12:03,309
We can only base our designs on them.

177
00:12:03,309 --> 00:12:05,020
Has Wang Jing not caught up yet?

178
00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:08,459
Our next ore conference will take place after next month.

179
00:12:08,459 --> 00:12:10,180
It's too slow.

180
00:12:11,070 --> 00:12:12,750
Do you see now?

181
00:12:13,689 --> 00:12:16,299
- See what?
- If it wasn't for the Single Rule,

182
00:12:16,299 --> 00:12:18,179
do you think it would've been like this?

183
00:12:18,179 --> 00:12:21,240
Then do you know why I made the rule?

184
00:12:21,890 --> 00:12:25,259
Because work shouldn't be affected by personal matters.

185
00:12:25,259 --> 00:12:28,540
What if we have more people like Wang Jing?

186
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:33,560
You can't lose something you never had.

187
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:36,849
Isn't it a slippery slope?

188
00:12:36,849 --> 00:12:38,830
Do you still want to argue?

189
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:46,109
Forget it. We have one more week to go.

190
00:12:46,109 --> 00:12:48,290
Just do it your way.

191
00:12:52,650 --> 00:12:55,359
Oh, can I contact Chairman Mai myself?

192
00:12:55,359 --> 00:12:58,269
I believe you're busy and short of time.

193
00:12:58,269 --> 00:13:02,700
I'll let you know if anything happens. What do you say?

194
00:13:25,940 --> 00:13:28,799
- Today's young people are really motivated.
- Chairman Mai.

195
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:31,719
You have contacted me very proactively. Take a seat.

196
00:13:31,719 --> 00:13:33,199
What is going on?

197
00:13:33,199 --> 00:13:36,740
Actually... I would like your opinion on something.

198
00:13:37,549 --> 00:13:39,629
Did Yu Zhen not come here with you?

199
00:13:39,629 --> 00:13:42,479
Our director... Chairman Mai, you know his personality.

200
00:13:42,479 --> 00:13:46,009
He's hard to get along with. When coordinating things with other people,

201
00:13:46,009 --> 00:13:48,129
- it takes quite a bit of time.
- What?

202
00:13:48,129 --> 00:13:51,659
Is Yu Zhen hard to get along with? No way.

203
00:13:51,659 --> 00:13:55,099
My impression of Yu Zhen is that he is very considerate

204
00:13:55,099 --> 00:13:57,480
and easy to communicate with.

205
00:13:58,780 --> 00:14:02,549
- It is quite different from what I see.
- Oh.

206
00:14:02,549 --> 00:14:05,010
Does this trouble you?

207
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:08,439
Do you need me to talk to him about this?

208
00:14:08,439 --> 00:14:10,649
No, no. Please don't bother.

209
00:14:10,649 --> 00:14:13,019
Our director has a high self-esteem

210
00:14:13,019 --> 00:14:16,699
so I don't think it is a good idea to talk to him directly.

211
00:14:16,699 --> 00:14:19,579
- You know him very well, don't you?
- No,

212
00:14:19,579 --> 00:14:22,659
I don't, but...

213
00:14:22,660 --> 00:14:26,890
- I do want to find out more about him.
- Why?

214
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:30,079
Be... because we are colleagues,

215
00:14:30,079 --> 00:14:33,399
plus, we are roommates.

216
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:36,699
I find it pretty good to know more about my roommate.

217
00:14:36,699 --> 00:14:38,860
So you live together.

218
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:42,040
You care about each other,

219
00:14:43,590 --> 00:14:45,870
