220
00:14:46,409 --> 00:14:48,080
Great!

221
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:54,989
I don't think he has changed.

222
00:14:54,989 --> 00:15:00,029
I noticed during the meeting that he also cared about you.

223
00:15:00,029 --> 00:15:02,349
- Did he?
- He surely did.

224
00:15:02,349 --> 00:15:06,339
For someone to throw themselves into work while also caring about other people

225
00:15:06,339 --> 00:15:09,119
is difficult indeed.

226
00:15:09,119 --> 00:15:10,819
