227
00:15:10,819 --> 00:15:13,019
But Chairman Mai, you don't seem like an inconsiderate person.

228
00:15:13,019 --> 00:15:17,019
You have no idea. When I was your age...

229
00:15:17,019 --> 00:15:20,089
I was ambitious and high-spirited.

230
00:15:20,089 --> 00:15:23,989
To develop my career, I worked so hard every single day.

231
00:15:23,989 --> 00:15:25,990
In the end,

232
00:15:26,649 --> 00:15:29,179
I lost my family,

233
00:15:29,179 --> 00:15:31,470
and also sacrificed my family.

234
00:15:32,650 --> 00:15:38,599
Now I don't even know how many times I can see my child in a year.

235
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:44,100
We haven't visited my wife's grave together in a long time.

236
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:49,629
That's why young people like you shouldn't be like me.

237
00:15:49,629 --> 00:15:53,220
Cherishing your family is the most important.

238
00:16:07,210 --> 00:16:10,249
- Are you busy?
- I am. Why?

239
00:16:10,249 --> 00:16:13,450
- What are you busy with?
- Learning new knowledge and keeping myself cultured.

240
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:15,499
I use this to process it.

241
00:16:15,499 --> 00:16:17,159
Knock it off.

242
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:19,750
I want to discuss something with you.

243
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:24,790
What is it?

244
00:16:26,650 --> 00:16:28,750
It's about Chairman Mai.

245
00:16:34,990 --> 00:16:40,639
Now I don't even know how many times I can see my child in a year.

246
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:45,000
We haven't visited my wife's grave together in a long time.

247
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,250
What do you want?

248
00:16:48,250 --> 00:16:50,390
I know that it's wrong to record it secretly, but I really—

249
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:53,399
Besides recording secretly, you even want to meddle in his affairs.

250
00:16:53,399 --> 00:16:56,249
How indifferent are you? Aren't you and Chairman Mai close?

251
00:16:56,249 --> 00:16:58,420
Yes, but he is also our client.

252
00:16:58,420 --> 00:17:02,849
I don't care about your motive behind this. Did you know that it disrespects our client?

253
00:17:02,849 --> 00:17:05,109
Fine. I disrespect him. I'm wrong.

254
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:08,840
- Are you happy now?
- Do you think I'm joking?

255
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:12,440
Do I look like I'm joking with you?

256
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:29,939
Listen to me.

257
00:17:29,939 --> 00:17:31,879
The only business between us and Chairman Mai

258
00:17:31,879 --> 00:17:34,249
is the proposal.

259
00:17:34,249 --> 00:17:37,059
Don't do anything unnecessary.

260
00:17:37,060 --> 00:17:40,630
Chairman Mai told me that you're a considerate person.

261
00:17:40,630 --> 00:17:42,669
No.

262
00:17:42,669 --> 00:17:45,219
But I think you are.

263
00:17:45,219 --> 00:17:47,189
I always believe in my instinct

264
00:17:47,189 --> 00:17:49,470
so I think you can help out with this.

265
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:51,270
What if I don't lift a finger?

266
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:55,559
- Then I'll look for Chairman Mai's family myself.
- You'll slow down the progress of the proposal.

267
00:17:55,559 --> 00:17:58,500
- I promise I won't.
- This determines the craft workshop's survival.

268
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:02,259
I understand, just like Wang Jing, Xiao Qian, and Si Qi.

269
00:18:02,259 --> 00:18:06,429
And even other people. I'm responsible for them because I'm their team leader.

270
00:18:06,429 --> 00:18:09,489
Similarly, I'm responsible for Chairman Mai as well.

271
00:18:09,489 --> 00:18:14,419
I'm aware that he accepted this proposal because he felt guilty about owing his family

272
00:18:14,419 --> 00:18:17,150
and wanted to make up for it.

273
00:18:21,970 --> 00:18:25,060
What if I stop you as the director?

274
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:32,029
Then I'll make a request to edit the proposal as the person in charge of this project.

275
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:55,610
♫ Several light years away, this journey is full of obstacles ♫

276
00:18:55,610 --> 00:18:59,900
♫ I'm unreasonable and sly like a devil in your eyes ♫

277
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:03,449
♫ Lifting our heads up suddenly, we're clearly out of the loop ♫

278
00:19:03,449 --> 00:19:07,759
♫ Show me. Show me. Your eyes ♫

279
00:19:07,759 --> 00:19:09,559
Chairman Mai replied to us.

280
00:19:09,559 --> 00:19:11,889
Here is the relevant information.

281
00:19:11,889 --> 00:19:14,040
Thank you.

282
00:19:14,040 --> 00:19:16,659
♫ I realize who doesn't care about the rights and wrongs ♫

283
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:19,609
♫ Hey, our last playing cards are on the table ♫

284
00:19:19,609 --> 00:19:24,289
♫ Hurry up and write down your promise. Don't change it ♫

285
00:19:24,289 --> 00:19:28,369
♫ In the next moment, tears are falling in the wind like drizzle ♫

286
00:19:28,369 --> 00:19:32,809
♫ When it's sunny, it's my turn to blow haze away for you ♫

287
00:19:32,809 --> 00:19:36,999
Wang Jing, do you have any information about copper wire wrapping that you can pass to me?

288
00:19:36,999 --> 00:19:41,639
And Xiao Qian, do you have any copper wire wrapping designs?

289
00:19:42,900 --> 00:19:45,070
Big Bro Lei's working so hard.

290
00:19:55,780 --> 00:19:57,599
This is the plan I have come up with so far,

291
00:19:57,599 --> 00:20:02,620
which considers mass production and avoids expensive ores that sell out easily.

292
00:20:02,620 --> 00:20:05,319
If it is not satisfactory, as long as Chairman Mai is willing to give me more time,

293
00:20:05,319 --> 00:20:07,500
I will definitely get it done to the best of my ability.

294
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:11,899
You're very thoughtful. Excellent.

295
00:20:11,899 --> 00:20:14,119
It is great indeed!

296
00:20:14,119 --> 00:20:16,919
Actually, I have another plan.

297
00:20:16,919 --> 00:20:20,319
- Oh?
- I was inspired by Chairman Mai.

298
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:23,490
Me? Did I give you any suggestions?

299
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:26,150
Hey.

300
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:32,300
This is designed specifically for Chairman Mai.

301
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:40,480
- This is...
- Please take a look, Chairman Mai.

302
00:20:57,510 --> 00:20:59,610
This is what my son drew.

303
00:21:02,390 --> 00:21:05,820
- Chairman Mai, I'm sorry about this—
- I took it upon myself.

304
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,390
Sorry.

305
00:21:15,870 --> 00:21:17,380
Dad,

306
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:23,349
how have you been?

307
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:25,519
Let's go visit mom's grave

308
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:28,040
on the long weekend of Qingming Festival.
(T/N: traditional Chinese tomb-sweeping festival)

309
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:57,549
You were so reckless.

310
00:21:57,549 --> 00:22:00,659
It's a good thing that Chairman Mai didn't hold you responsible for recording him secretly.

311
00:22:00,659 --> 00:22:03,250
Otherwise, even I couldn't protect you.

312
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:09,309
I was going to take some of the responsibility,

313
00:22:09,309 --> 00:22:11,799
but I didn't know he liked you so much.

314
00:22:11,799 --> 00:22:14,989
In the end, I looked like I was trying to take credit.

315
00:22:14,989 --> 00:22:17,980
Don't worry. You can take the credit.

316
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:26,860
Why are you so quiet today? It's not like you.

317
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:32,940
Hey! Hey!

318
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:39,820
Feels so hot.

319
00:22:46,180 --> 00:22:49,270
♫ I do! I do! I do ♫

320
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:55,559
♫ Because I do! I do! I do ♫

321
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:57,829
♫ The coffee shop on the street corner ♫

322
00:22:57,829 --> 00:23:00,189
♫ Has the smell of bubbles ♫

323
00:23:00,189 --> 00:23:02,859
♫ I have an indescribable gut feeling ♫

324
00:23:02,860 --> 00:23:05,099
♫ That I may run into someone today ♫

325
00:23:05,099 --> 00:23:07,399
♫ It's finally on the hour ♫

326
00:23:07,399 --> 00:23:09,849
♫ The streets are ablaze with color as usual ♫

327
00:23:09,849 --> 00:23:12,349
♫ Feeling romantic in the breeze alongside the river ♫

328
00:23:12,349 --> 00:23:14,689
♫ I can't help spinning excitedly ♫

329
00:23:14,689 --> 00:23:17,719
♫ The midnight showing got delayed ♫

330
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:21,749
♫ That day you made a promise ♫

331
00:23:21,749 --> 00:23:24,539
♫ And I wished upon a shooting star ♫

332
00:23:24,539 --> 00:23:27,539
♫ Your face profile, smile and eyes ♫

333
00:23:27,539 --> 00:23:31,500
♫ Are irresistible ♫

334
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:34,390
♫ I'm gonna share with you, my love ♫

335
00:23:34,390 --> 00:23:36,349
♫ I do, do, do ♫

336
00:23:36,349 --> 00:23:38,659
♫ We've promised to meet again in early summer ♫

337
00:23:38,659 --> 00:23:41,009
♫ With the wings that brought us together ♫

338
00:23:41,009 --> 00:23:44,879
♫ I'll fly when sunshine comes after rain ♫

339
00:23:44,879 --> 00:23:47,289
Where do you want to go?

340
00:23:47,290 --> 00:23:49,259
You can't leave

341
00:23:49,259 --> 00:23:51,909
without an explanation.

342
00:23:51,910 --> 00:23:54,360
♫ Every best moment ♫
